title: Hanin Elias - Future Noir (2004)
description:
HANIN ELIAS
Future Noir

2004 studio album from the ex-Atari Teenage Riot singer. Best described as Blade Runner-Esque Future Noir Sound. Featuring special guest Thurston Moore! Fatal.
